"{\"uid\": \"scmp.com-magazines-style-people-celebrities-article-3263086-gabby-douglas-paris-olympics-2024-comeback-all-around-champion-us-gymnast-won-gold-medals-both\", \"entities\": [{\"sentence\": \"The gymnastics veteran has swept up plenty of accolades throughout her career, taking home the All-Around Champion title at her first Summer Olympic Games in London in 2012 and leading the US team to victory at Rio de Janeiro in 2016.\", \"from\": 0, \"to\": 234, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 158, \"end\": 164, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/London\", \"score\": 0.9997869458895507, \"rank\": 0.00020190588639325613, \"text\": \"London\", \"types\": [\"Q515\", \"Q486972\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/London\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/London\"}, {\"begin\": 189, \"end\": 191, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/United_States_men's_national_basketball_team\", \"score\": 0.9999999482328135, \"rank\": 5.1684031232196826e-08, \"text\": \"US\", \"types\": [], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/United_States_men's_national_basketball_team\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/United_States_men's_national_basketball_team\"}, {\"begin\": 211, \"end\": 225, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Rio_de_Janeiro\", \"score\": 0.9999999920635219, \"rank\": 7.911636239527863e-09, \"text\": \"Rio de Janeiro\", \"types\": [\"Q486972\", \"Q3957\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Rio_de_Janeiro\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Rio_de_Janeiro\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"She also won gold medals both in 2012 and 2016 as part of the \\\"Fierce Five\\\" and \\\"Final Five\\\" of the US women's team in artistic gymnastics - and nabbed the title of World All-Around silver medallist at the young age of 20.\", \"from\": 236, \"to\": 458, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 336, \"end\": 338, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/United_States_men's_national_basketball_team\", \"score\": 0.9999999482328135, \"rank\": 5.1684031232196826e-08, \"text\": \"US\", \"types\": [], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/United_States_men's_national_basketball_team\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/United_States_men's_national_basketball_team\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Recently, she was the oldest gymnast at the US Winter Cup in February, and went head to head with Suni Lee and Simone Biles at the US Classic in May.\", \"from\": 460, \"to\": 609, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 558, \"end\": 566, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Sunisa_Lee\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 0.0, \"text\": \"Suni Lee\", \"types\": [\"Q729\", \"Q5\", \"Q215627\", \"Q19088\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Sunisa_Lee\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Sunisa_Lee\"}, {\"begin\": 571, \"end\": 583, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Simone_Biles\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 0.0, \"text\": \"Simone Biles\", \"types\": [\"Q729\", \"Q5\", \"Q215627\", \"Q19088\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Simone_Biles\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Simone_Biles\"}, {\"begin\": 591, \"end\": 593, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/United_States_men's_national_basketball_team\", \"score\": 0.9999999482328135, \"rank\": 5.1684031232196826e-08, \"text\": \"US\", \"types\": [], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/United_States_men's_national_basketball_team\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/United_States_men's_national_basketball_team\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Her wins were not only milestone moments for the gymnast herself - they marked a significant era in her sport.\", \"from\": 611, \"to\": 721, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"Douglas is the first African-American to take home the title of individual All-Around Champion at the Olympics - and the only American at the time to also bring home the same title for team competitions in 2012.\", \"from\": 722, \"to\": 933, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 722, \"end\": 729, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Katie_Douglas\", \"score\": 0.5336571729051472, \"rank\": 0.7539564021942559, \"text\": \"Douglas\", \"types\": [\"Q729\", \"Q5\", \"Q3665646\", \"Q215627\", \"Q19088\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Katie_Douglas\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Katie_Douglas\"}, {\"begin\": 743, \"end\": 759, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/African_Americans\", \"score\": 0.9999652610825538, \"rank\": 1.7437267244942467e-05, \"text\": \"African-American\", \"types\": [\"Q41710\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/African_Americans\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/African_Americans\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"So what else do we know about her?\", \"from\": 935, \"to\": 969, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"Like many American athletes, the 28-year-old's success in the arena translated to fame in pop culture.\", \"from\": 971, \"to\": 1073, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"In the tradition of American Olympians, Douglas appeared on the box of Kellogg's cornflakes cereal, inspiring a whole generation of gymnastic hopefuls.\", \"from\": 1074, \"to\": 1225, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 1114, \"end\": 1121, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Katie_Douglas\", \"score\": 0.5336571729051472, \"rank\": 0.7539564021942559, \"text\": \"Douglas\", \"types\": [\"Q729\", \"Q5\", \"Q3665646\", \"Q215627\", \"Q19088\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Katie_Douglas\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Katie_Douglas\"}, {\"begin\": 1145, \"end\": 1152, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Kellogg's\", \"score\": 0.9999996102271402, \"rank\": 2.4478576271229027e-07, \"text\": \"Kellogg\", \"types\": [\"Q4830453\", \"Q43229\", \"Q24229398\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Kellogg's\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Kellogg's\"}]}]}"